This is a base of problems for Kharkiv winter camp on computer programming.
The topic is geometry 3d.

Div 1.
Find a plane dividing a set of points in two equal parts.
Find an intersection of a line and a plane.
Find distance between two segments.
Convex hull n^4.
Dodecahedron.
Phantom.

Div 2.
Sniper.
Convex hull n^2.
Pyramids.
Threed.
Phantom (n <= 1000)

Div 3.
Convex hull nlog(n).
Orange cutting.
Phantom (n <= 1000)
If two polyhedra intersects.
Minkovsky.
Intersection.
